import React from 'react'
import {BrowserRouter, Routes, Route} from 'react-router-dom'
import Login from './pages/Login'
import Register from './pages/Register'
import NotFound from './pages/NotFound'
import {
  AddClub,
  EditClub,
  Clubs,
  Club,
  Shots,
  // EditShot,
  // AllShots,
  // AddShot,
} from './pages/index'
import LandingPage from './pages/LandingPage'
import Shot from './pages/shots/Shot'

const App = () => {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
      <Routes>
        <Route path='/' element={<LandingPage />} />
        <Route path='/clubs' element={<Clubs />} />
        <Route path='/clubs/addclub' element={<AddClub />} />
        <Route path='/clubs/viewclub/:id' element={<Club />} />
        <Route path='/clubs/editclub/:id' element={<EditClub />} />
        <Route path='/login' element={<Login />} />
        <Route path='/register' element={<Register />} />
        <Route path='/*' element={<NotFound />} />

        <Route path='/shots' element={<Shots />}>
          <Route path=':shotid' element={<Shot />} />
          {/* <Route path=':new' element={<AddShot />} /> */}
        </Route>
      </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}

export default App
